* Naming Patterns\nfor Data Organization
** Use lowercase with underscores
***_ customer_data, sales_summary
***_ Avoid camelCase / PascalCase
** Be descriptive but concise
***_ sales_summary_gold ✓
***_ sales_final_report_v1_updated ✗
** Medallion architecture
***_ bronze = raw data
***_ silver = cleaned data
***_ gold = aggregated data
** Prefix specialized objects
***_ vw_ for views
***_ tmp_ for staging tables
** Catalog naming strategy
***_ Domain-based: sales_data, finance_data
***_ Environment-based: dev, test, prod
@endmindmap
